data.description:
NEW Construction completed 5/25/18. Backs to large ranch. Unbelievable covered front and back decks.  Back covered deck provides about 256 square feet of private outdoor living space!  Custom high quality storage shed.  drive way wide enough for 2 large trucks.  Beautiful wooded lot in the COUNTY but so close to Granbury shopping.
3 bedrooms (split) with 2 full baths.  Large walk in closets.  Lovely wood look vinyl flooring in laundry, kitchen, dining, baths, and back bedroom. Energy efficient; insulation, HVAC, ceiling fans, shade trees, thermal windows, and the covered porches. Great community amenities; pool, playground, parks, club house, private boat launch to Lake Granbury with park, picnic tables, temporary boat tie off locations. Fha Mortgage approved foundation and wood skirting to match exterior.
data.whatILove:
NEW Construction!  Be the first to call this house your HOME!  Backs to a large ranch.  Enjoy a private back yard in the county but so close to town.  The lot was cleared to keep as many trees as possible and still place the house, NEW aerobic septic system, and front and back covered porches/decks.  This will be a very energy efficient home; 2018 construction/insulation, shade trees, and covered porches, and thermal windows that open to clean from the inside!  A custom built wood storage shed with metal roof will also be provided.  I can also show you an example of this product as it is not on the lot as of 4/25/18.  
 NOTE:  porches and drive way are IN PROCESS of being complete.  I do have completed model to show you located in Sky Harbour neighborhood so you can see the QUALITY of product provided.  
GREAT neighborhood amenities; pool, club house, parks and boat launch/with temporary tie off area and park.
HOA dues for the 2 lots included are $210/lot/year. 
Home includes Refrigerator/freezer with water output to fridge, dishwasher and electric range.  Ceiling fan in family room, Mini blinds in all rooms. Sliding Glass door to back deck, china sinks in master and hall bath!  Large walk in closets in all bedrooms.
Prefer cash buyer but the home was constructed with Fha Financing in mind; concrete footing row foundation and Fha approved skirting.
Skirting is also wood that will be painted to match wood siding.
